questionText: How long have you had diabetes?
hint: What is the circumference of your waist at its narrowest point?

questionText: how many minutes do you exercise per day, on average?
How many servings of fruits and vegetables do you average each day?
How many meals did you eat at a fast food or convenience store?
hint: This includes doughnut shops, sandwich shops, and coffee shops.
answerSuffix: total meals at a fast food or convenience store in the last 7 days

questionText: How many sweet beverages did you drink per day?
hint: Please estimate your average daily intake of sweet beverages like fruit juices and soft drinks.

questionText: How many evening snacks did you eat?
hint: This includes any food you ate after the evening meal.
answerSuffix: total evening snacks in the last 7 days

questionText: How many servings of meat did you eat per day?
hint: A serving of meat is 3 ounces (about 1/3 of a cup) of beef, fish, poultry, pork, or other animal product.

questionText: How many meals did you that were NOT home-prepared?
hint: A home-prepared meal is a meal that was prepared at home.
answerSuffix: total meals that were NOT prepared at home

questionText: How many times did you buy your lunch?
How many sweet snacks did you eat per day?
hint: Please estimate your average daily intake of sweet snacks like ice cream (half cup per serving), cookies (2 Oreo cookies per serving).
answerSuffix: servings per day of sweet snacks

questionText: How many servings of dairy did you eat per day?
hint: A serving of dairy is one cup of milk or yogurt, 2 ounces of cheese, or a half cup of ice cream, cottage cheese, or pudding
answerSuffix: servings of dairy products per day

questionText: How many servings of junk food did you eat?
hint: Junk food is like art.  You know it when you see it.
answerSuffix: servings per day of junk food

questionText: On a scale of 0 (worst possible) to 10 (best possible), please rate the overall quality and quantity of sleep you have had.
answerPrefix: I rate my overall sleep at

questionText: How many hours of sleep did you get per 24 hours?
hint: Please estimate your average daily sleep over the last 7 days.

questionText: Have you gone through menopause ("the change of life")?
How many times do you overeat in a week?
hint: Overeating means you felt too full after eating.
